  "analyticalMethod": "HPLC, GC-MS, UV-Vis",
  "qualityGrade": "Ph.Eur., USP, ChP",
  "profileNotes": {
    "en": "Commercial turmeric typically contains 2-5% curcuminoids (curcumin, demethoxycurcumin, bisdemethoxycurcumin). Curcumin content varies with cultivar (Alleppey, Madras, etc.) and growing conditions."
